About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Kollam Sudhi was a beloved comedian in the Malayalam entertainment industry who left a lasting impact on his audiences. In this emotional talk, his wife Renu Sudhi speaks candidly about her life with Kollam Sudhi, sharing heartwarming anecdotes and memories. She also touches on the challenges they faced as a family and how they overcame them together. This powerful and touching talk is a tribute to the legacy of Kollam Sudhi, and a must-watch for anyone who loved him. Join us as we celebrate the life and work of this remarkable artist.

snippet.title: Gulab Jamun with Instant Gulab Jamun Mix Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make gulab jamun recipe in tamil. This gulab jamun is made with instant jamun mix. This is very easy to make only requires milk and sugar. The gulab jamun mix can be used in place of mava / khoya. We can use coconut flakes and other nuts to decorate and add texture to these spongy gulab jamuns.
#gulabjamun #gulabjamunrecipe #gulabjamunwithmix 

Friends, please do try this gulab jamun recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Spread the joy cooking during this festival season. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking. 

Wishing everyone a very happy Diwali and enjoy this festival season with homemade sweets.

175g Instant Gulab Jamun mix (1.5 cup)
1/2 cup Milk approx
3 cup Sugar
3 cup Water
few Saffron
Cardamom powder
1/2 tsp Ghee

snippet.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Always remember who you are‚Ä¶

The four nations of the world once lived in harmony, with the Avatar, master of all four elements, keeping peace between them. But everything changed when the Fire Nation attacked and wiped out the Air Nomads, the first step taken by the firebenders towards conquering the world.

AVATAR: THE LAST AIRBENDER, follows a young Air Nomad named Aang, as he reawakens to a world ravaged by war. Together with his newfound friends Sokka and Katara, he embarks on an action-packed quest to take his rightful place as the next AVATAR.

This new live-action reimagining of the award-winning Nickelodeon animated series comes to Netflix in 2024.

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. snippet.title: Sam‡§¨‡§π‡§æ‡§¶‡•Å‡§∞ - Official Trailer | Vicky Kaushal | Meghna Gulzar | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 01.12.2023
snippet.description:
To the Indian army, to the nation and its people, we present to you a glimpse into the life of India's Greatest Soldier, Sam Manekshaw. 

#SamBahadur Trailer Out Now! 
#Sam‡§¨‡§π‡§æ‡§¶‡•Å‡§∞ in cinemas 1.12.2023

#SamIsHere 

Sam‡§¨‡§π‡§æ‡§¶‡•Å‡§∞ is a tribute to Field Marshal Sam HFJ Manekshaw, MC, India's first Field Marshal and a legendary Army General. His career witnessed the shaping of India's geopolitical borders, and his life was marked by significant milestones, from fighting in World War II to being the Chief of Army Staff during the 1971 Indo-Pakistan war, that led to the creation of Bangladesh.
This RSVP film explores his dynamic personality and his unparalleled military career, offering a glimpse into the life of a no-nonsense Army Commander, also known as "Sam Bahadur" by the soldiers he led.

snippet.description:

Episode 3925: Jethalal Ka Sapna Toota
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is devastated after MRP was shown to be a hoax since he had hoped to purchase a lunar plot for Babita. He contacts Taarak for assistance, but Taarak appears to be preoccupied with work, despite Jetha's persistent nagging. Taarak ultimately decides to assist Jetha and arrives at his business. Jetha informs Bagha and Nattu Kaka that MRP is a bogus firm. Bagha becomes discouraged and attacks Jetha, but Nattu Kaka urges him to calm down. What would Jetha bestow upon Babita?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3924: Sapna Reh Gaya Sapna
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha hears someone calling him out while the Gokuldham villagers joyfully celebrate Garba. Later, Jetha finds that he has been fantasizing about buying the lunar plot and delivering it to Babita all along. Anyway, he finally arrives at the MRP office, and before entering, he contacts Champaklal to wish him well. Jetha also calls Babita and asks her to be present at her house, as he plans to surprise her with his enigmatic gift. Jetha enters the MRP office, but he is taken aback when he sees Popatlal and Chalu Pandey.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3924, 9 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Diwali Special Access: Takeshi‚Äôs Castle - Episode 1 | @BBKiVines  | Prime Video India

With joy and laughter, this festive season we are presenting the first episode of Takeshi‚Äôs Castle dubbed in Hindi by Bhuvan Bam. Relive your childhood memories with the classic games and new terrifying obstacles. Watch all episodes available only on Prime Video India.

Watch Now - https://bit.ly/TakeshisCastleOnPrime

Bhuvan Bam lends his distinctive voice and unique humor as commentator in the brand-new season of Takeshi's Castle. Classic games are making a comeback with new and terrifying obstacles emerging one after another. The lord of the castle, Beat Takeshi, entrusts Bananaman to protect it. Subaru Kimura is the attack force‚Äôs new leader. The elite team gathers to bring down the revived Takeshi‚Äôs Castle.

Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ‚Çπ1499/ year.

Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video‚Äôs exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ‚Çπ599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website.

Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.

The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Episode 3923: Babita Ke Liye Best Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha ultimately tells the inhabitants of Gokuldham about his surprise present for Babita. Jetha dims the lights and produces a lunar-like atmosphere, which surprises everyone. Babita is ecstatic after learning that Jetha has some exciting plans for the actual Moon. Jetha informs Babita that he has purchased a lunar plot for her. Champaklal is taken aback and queries Jetha about it. Other Gokuldham people are skeptical about Jetha's words. Later, Bagha and Nattu Kaka disclose everything to everyone in order to back up Jetha's claim.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3923, 8 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: IND Beat SA: Kohli's Triple Blast, Shoaib Akhtar Shocked! | Aakash Chopra Reaction | World Cup 2023
snippet.description:
India Beats South Africa World Cup 2023 Live Updates: In the match played between India and South Africa in the World Cup 2023, India has defeated South Africa. Batting first, Team India had given a target of 327 runs to South Africa to win. In response to which South African team was out within 100 runs. Kohli played a century for India. Shreyas Iyer played an inning of 77 runs. On the bowling front, Ravindra Jadeja took 5 wickets and Kuldeep took 2 wickets. The entire South African team could score only 83 runs. The 243-run victory, which came on the occasion of Virat Kohli's birthday, was spectacular.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.description:
The third episode of Koffee with Karan season 8 goes on air, featuring Sara Ali Khan and Ananya Panday to deliver some drama and spill too many coffee beans. These two are the new besties in the B-town, sharing more than just an ex-boyfriend.

While Sara exposed the lies about the industry, we also discovered a possessive, blushing and shy Ananya who is currently dating the Aashiqui boy ‚ÄòAditya Roy Kapur‚Äô.

From box office failure to Shubman Gill and then threatening Ananya, Sara Ali Khan gave insights to all things personal. On the other hand, Ananya got real about how she has only worked to get the validation and respect of people around.

Not just that, Karan Johar himself opened up about his friendships in the industry, who he is close to and how he managed the friend equation when they turned sour.
